snippet.title: Irina Shayk & Amber Heard Stun In Barely-There Ensembles At The 2018 Cannes Film Festival
snippet.description:
Irina Shayk and Amber Heard took bold fashion risks for the "Sorry Angel" premiere on Day 3 of the 2018 Cannes Film Festival. The supermodel left little to the imagination in a racy Versace number, while the "Justice League" actress took the plunge in a low-cut Valentino gown. See their sexy red carpet looks!
